PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>
PREFIX :<http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX dbpedia2:<http://dbpedia.org/property>
PREFIX dbpedia:<http://dbpedia.org/>
PREFIX dbpedia3:<http://dbpedia.org/ontology>

SELECT distinct
?name ?birth ?person WHERE 
{?person dbpedia2:birthPlace <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin>.
?person dbpedia2:birth ?birth. 
?person faof: name ? name
} ORDER BY ?name

PREFIX dbpedia2:<http://dbpedia.org/property>
PREFIX dbpedia:<http://dbpedia.org/>
PREFIX dbpedia3:<http://dbpedia.org/ontology>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>
PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?nom ?image ?description
WHERE {
        ?personne rdf:type foaf:Person.
        ?personne foaf:name ?nom.
        ?image rdf:type foaf:Image.
        ?personne foaf:img ?image.
        ?image dc:description ?description
}

PREFIX dbpedia2:<http://dbpedia.org/property>
PREFIX dbpedia:<http://dbpedia.org/>
PREFIX dbpedia3:<http://dbpedia.org/ontology>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>
PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?nom ?image ?description
WHERE {
        ?personne rdf:type foaf:Person.
        ?personne foaf:name ?nom.
        ?image rdf:type foaf:Image.
        ?personne foaf:img ?image.
        ?image dc:description ?description
}

PREFIX dbpo:<http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX type:<http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/>
PREFIX prop:<http://dbpedia.org/property/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?x
WHERE {
     ?x a dbpedia-owl:Person.
     rdfs:label ?occupation;
     prop:occupation ?guitarist;
     rdfs:label ?birthPlace.
     ?x dbpedia-owl:birthPlace dbpedia:Boston.
     FILTER regex(?occupation} LIMIT 100

PREFIX dbpo:<http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX type:<http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/>
PREFIX prop:<http://dbpedia.org/property/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?x
WHERE {
     ?x a dbpo:MusicalArtist.
     dbpo:instrument ?instrument.
     dbpo:birthPlace ?birthPlace.
     FILTER regex(?instrument, "guitare", "i").
     FILTER regex(?birthPlace, "Boston", "i").
} LIMIT 100

PREFIX dbpo:<http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?x
FROM <dbpedia.org>
WHERE {
     ?x a dbpo:MusicalArtist.
     dbpo:instrument ?instrument.
     dbpo:birthPlace ?birthPlace.
     FILTER regex (?instrument, "guitare", "i").
     FILTER regex (?birthPlace, "Boston", "i").
}
